      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor, including documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal valve timing. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction, while the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings. This is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car, free of common structural gremlins and ready for high-RPM engagement.",
