      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior shines in a deep Midnight Blue metallic finish, showing only minor signs of road use like small stone chips consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the premium charcoal leather upholstery remains supple and clean, with all electronic features\u2014from the heated seats to the high-definition infotainment system\u2014functioning flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent oil change. It handles beautifully on its 19-inch alloy wheels, which are wrapped in tires with significant tread remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been primarily garage-kept and is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
